  "id": "8c652145da1346ea875412167c6e4d76",
  "title": "Smooth Camera Kit",
  "description": "An easy-to-implement solution for your Topdown and Sidescroller games!",
  "longDescription": "<p>Video: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#61;GUjXGUOgnKU\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#61;GUjXGUOgnKU</a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>UPDATE: NOW SUPPORTS MULTIPLAYER - Preview: </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/PandaDevStudios/status/947177225908113408\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>https://twitter.com/PandaDevStudios/status/947177225908113408</em></a></p><p><br /></p><p><strong><em>UPDATE: Now support available on our </em></strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/aUGYP7P\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><em>Discord</em></strong></a><strong><em> </em></strong></p><p><br /></p><p>Do you need a solution for your topdown and/or side scroller games? An easy-to-implement kit that will handle your camera for you? Look no further!</p><p>Including 3 different camera modes for both location and rotation and 10&#43; settings you can customize your camera for almost every scenario!</p><p><br /></p><p>Including Static(Camera remains on one location), Non-Instant(camera travels further or less far than the character) ,Instant(basic camera with follow lag) or Spline mode(follows closest location on spline from pawn)and rotation modes</p><p>of Character(Follow char with pitch and yaw), Character-Z(Follow pitch only) and Static(Look at a static point).</p><p><br /></p><p>Coming with a topdown and sidecroller template and example content for you to try out different premade presets.</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>BPs: 5</p><p>Levels: 2</p><p>Presets: 7</p><p><br /></p><p>Info:</p><p>Documentation included: True</p><p>Multiplayer: Cameras are controlled locally, no replication happening.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Tested Platform: Windows</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.saltypandastudios.com/docs/smoothcamera/setup\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://docs.saltypandastudios.com/docs/smoothcamera/setup</a></p><p><br /></p><p>Do you want to stay updated on new releases, sales and more? <a href=\"http://eepurl.com/bMlEHb\" rel=\"nofollow\">Subscribe to our newsletter!</a></p><p><br /></p><p>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PandaDevStudios\" rel=\"nofollow\"> https://twitter.com/PandaDevStudios </a></p><p>Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PandaDevStudios/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> https://www.facebook.com/PandaDevStudios/</a></p><p>Forum thread: <a href=\"https://forums.unrealengine.com/showthread.php?148858-Smooth-Camera-Kit-2-%285%29D-and-Topdown-camera-solution-for-your-game!\" rel=\"nofollow\"> https://forums.unrealengine.com/showthread.php?148858-Smooth-Camera-Kit-2-(5)D-and-Topdown-camera-solution-for-your-game!</a></p><p>Website: <a href=\"https://panda-studios.net/wp/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> https://panda-studios.net/wp/ </a></p>",
